Package: dominoClaudeRus
Title: Claude-Powered RStudio Addins for Clinical Programming on Domino
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Wasantha", "Gamage",
    email = "wasantha.gamage@dominodatalab.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: RStudio addins that integrate Claude Code CLI into clinical
    programming workflows for teams working in Domino workspaces. Provides
    AI-assisted tools for R log analysis, CDISC data inspection, warning
    remediation, Statistical Analysis Plan (SAP) review, and Domino job
    configuration — all accessible directly from the RStudio Addins menu
    without leaving the IDE.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    rstudioapi (>= 0.13),
    utils
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/dominodatalab/domino-blueprints/tree/main/dominoClaudeRus
BugReports: https://github.com/dominodatalab/domino-blueprints/issues
